class FgRegister:
    """
    The `FgRegister` class provides a set of predefined foreground color styles for use in terminal output, including classic colors and less commonly supported extended colors. Each style is accessible as an attribute of an instance of this class. The available colors include standard black, red, green, yellow, blue, magenta, cyan, light grey, dark grey, lighter shades of the basic colors, and least supported deep shades of these colors.

    Attributes:
        black (Style): Style for black foreground color.
        red (Style): Style for red foreground color.
        green (Style): Style for green foreground color.
        yellow (Style): Style for yellow foreground color.
        blue (Style): Style for blue foreground color.
        magenta (Style): Style for magenta foreground color.
        cyan (Style): Style for cyan foreground color.
